1: Inception & Data

Finalize scope (single city MVP).

Ingest Kaggle hotel/POI datasets, clean, load to Supabase.

Set up embeddings + hybrid search.

2: Orchestration & Tools

Implement /plan endpoint and tool functions.

First prompt templates; itinerary heuristic.

3: Frontend MVP

Trip Wizard + Chat; hotel picker; save/load trips.

Basic map/day timeline.

4: Eval & Polish

Add feedback loop; telemetry; improve prompts.

Pilot test with 10 users; fix top issues.

Stretch (Weeks 5–6): multi‑city, personalization, weather/events.
